  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Prospective observational study to evaluate the impact of Recto-Anal-Repair (a technique of
      ultrasound guided haemorrhoidal ligation) in the treatment of stage III/IV haemorrhoidal
      disease.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
